{
  "stem": "26111.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So if it had been the other way around, the getting out of hell would have been-- the joy of that would have been ruined by-- might have been ruined by, my worry about, yes, but no, I won't go if I have to leave you behind, et cetera, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So there was no-- there was none of that, in that sense.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not resist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did  not resist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I, I, I had all kinds of-- kinds of objections.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And certainly, I did say these things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What if this doesn't happen, if you can't get out, et cetera?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I didn't know everything that they were doing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when he said, we're doing a lot of things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We're going to get out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of them is going to come off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, he was a very convincing person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, in the same way that I respected him as a person, his intellect, his, his power of, of, of thought, I, I, I had to respect what he was saying because this was serious-- this was serious talk about serious matters.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes, indeed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really, no.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had some idea that this was being organized by Jewish committees in England and that, somehow, we would be taken care of-- the children would be taken care of.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] England was not that much of an unknown to me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I should say very quickly that at the Goldschmidt Schule-- School, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Mrs.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Goldschmidt had, had the foresight-- in '36 I think, already, maybe early '37-- to make contact with the Cambridge University in England and to convince them to appoint her school an examination center of the university in Germany, the first, first center.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
